  :name, :tagline, :description }</p>
  <pre>/api/v1/users</pre>

  <br />

  <h4>
    Items List 
    <a href="/api/v1/items?api_key=123456789" target="_blank">
      <i class="fa fa-fw fa-arrow-circle-right"></i>
    </a>
  </h4>
  <p>Returns a list of 20 random Items with the following parameters:
  <br /> :id, :title, :category, :color, :code, :user_id, :created_at</p>
  <pre>/api/v1/items</pre>
  <p>Also accepts the options <strong>limit</strong> and <strong>user_id</strong>, which will limit the number of items returned (max: 50) and set the user_id, respectively.</p>
